<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 01:22:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于伊朗乐观情绪，比特币结束了连续五个月的下跌</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-btc-rises-with-risk-assets-as-trump-talks-end-of-iran-war</link><description>随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普和伊朗表示愿意结束中东冲突，比特币打破了长达五个月的连续下跌，录得自 9 月份以来的首次月度上涨。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i64i8N6HqTi8/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 05:13:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-btc-rises-with-risk-assets-as-trump-talks-end-of-iran-war</guid></item><item><title>加密货币的周末交易平台被证明是有先见之明的</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-31/crypto-s-weekend-trading-venues-are-proving-to-be-prescient</link><description>打开定价冲突的窗口&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iiSNGfkkJblQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-31/crypto-s-weekend-trading-venues-are-proving-to-be-prescient</guid></item><item><title>Block 的 Dorsey 概述了人工智能驱动的削减中层管理人员的愿景</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/block-s-dorsey-outlines-ai-powered-vision-to-cut-middle-managers</link><description>在 Block Inc. 宣布裁员近一半后几周，杰克·多尔西 (Jack Dorsey) 在重新构想科技公司应如何运作的观点中，将人工智能作为中层管理人员的替代品。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i228Gfmczcvc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 19:05:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/block-s-dorsey-outlines-ai-powered-vision-to-cut-middle-managers</guid></item><item><title>比特币支持的市政债券扫清了穆迪评级的障碍</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-backed-municipal-bond-clears-hurdle-with-moody-s-rating</link><description>风险最高的资产类别正在与同类中最安全的金融产品之一融合：比特币支持的市政债券。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i53JkSgE1_dA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 18:58:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-backed-municipal-bond-clears-hurdle-with-moody-s-rating</guid></item><item><title>Tether 从汇丰银行聘请黄金交易员几个月后裁员</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/tether-cuts-top-gold-traders-months-after-hiring-them-from-hsbc</link><description>Tether Holdings SA 在从汇丰控股有限公司聘用两名高级贵金属交易员几个月后，裁掉了两名高级贵金属交易员，以创建所谓的“世界上最好的黄金交易大厅”。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3Yp1BMvIAoY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 12:17:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/tether-cuts-top-gold-traders-months-after-hiring-them-from-hsbc</guid></item><item><title>帕内塔表示欧洲央行必须避免战争引发的工资价格螺旋式上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/ecb-s-panetta-says-private-sector-key-in-cross-border-payments</link><description>欧洲央行管理委员会成员法比奥·帕内塔表示，官员们不能让战争驱动的通胀推高工资，同时警告不要做出过于强烈的反应。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iaUstt.aNd.c/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 15:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/ecb-s-panetta-says-private-sector-key-in-cross-border-payments</guid></item><item><title>Cross River 融资 5000 万美元，进一步进军人工智能和加密领域</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/cross-river-raises-50-million-to-expand-further-into-ai-crypto</link><description>据彭博社审阅的一份声明称，随着这家专注于金融科技的银行加倍投资人工智能和加密货币，Cross River Bank 已向现有投资者筹集了 5000 万美元的新资本。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNd_baPre8LU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/cross-river-raises-50-million-to-expand-further-into-ai-crypto</guid></item><item><title>大卫·贝利 (David Bailey) 的中本聪出售一些比特币以资助运营</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/david-bailey-s-nakamoto-sells-some-bitcoin-to-fund-operations</link><description>购买并持有比特币的 Nakamoto Holdings Inc. 本月出售了价值 2000 万美元的比特币，尽管该代币较峰值下跌了近 50%。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/icNEKr3vpL_w/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 05:50:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/david-bailey-s-nakamoto-sells-some-bitcoin-to-fund-operations</guid></item><item><title>加密货币交易所 KuCoin 向 CFTC 支付 50 万美元以结束民事案件</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/crypto-exchange-kucoin-pays-cftc-500-000-to-end-civil-case</link><description>加密货币交易所 KuCoin 的运营商将支付 50 万美元，以和解美国衍生品监管机构对其运营未注册离岸平台、非法让美国居民进行交易的指控。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i5.khmz.KgEo/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 23:23:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/crypto-exchange-kucoin-pays-cftc-500-000-to-end-civil-case</guid></item><item><title>拟议的共和党法案针对外国加密货币挖矿硬件</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/proposed-gop-bill-targets-foreign-crypto-mining-hardware</link><description>共和党参议员周一公布了一项法案，旨在阻止美国加密货币挖矿公司使用与中国和其他外国对手相关的设备。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ijjebIvf72ZE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 22:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/proposed-gop-bill-targets-foreign-crypto-mining-hardware</guid></item><item><title>执法负责人辞职后参议员就加密货币问题向 SEC 提出质询</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/senator-queries-sec-on-crypto-cases-after-enforcement-head-quits</link><description>两名美国参议员希望证券交易委员会主席保罗·阿特金斯解释其执行主任的突然辞职，以及她的离职是否与加密货币案件有关，其中包括涉及特朗普家族企业的案件。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihCjjTkzOkw4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 18:41:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/senator-queries-sec-on-crypto-cases-after-enforcement-head-quits</guid></item><item><title>Saylor 的策略在连续 13 周购买比特币后崩溃</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/saylor-s-strategy-takes-break-after-13-weeks-of-bitcoin-buying</link><description>就在公布筹集 420 亿美元以支持其购买比特币的计划几天后，Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 在连续 13 次每周宣布购买加密货币后暂停了交易。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iSxa0aAGSFxw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 13:39:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-30/saylor-s-strategy-takes-break-after-13-weeks-of-bitcoin-buying</guid></item></channel></rss>